snippet.title: Super Alpha Iguanodon Gameplay | Showcase - Dinosaur King Awaken Arcade Game 恐竜キング
snippet.description:
Dinosaur King Awaken Showcase 1 - Super Alpha Iguanodon
ft. Ursula VS Dr. Spike Taylor

Super Alpha Iguanodon 超アクト恐竜 イグアノドン 超級亞法黨恐龍 禽龍
Element : Grass 草
Strength : 1600
Name Meaning : Iguana Tooth
Length: 10m
[ https://dinosaurking.fandom.com/wiki/Iguanodon/Alpha ]

VS

Tuojiangosaurus & Gigantspinosaurus

I gonna make a series of dinosaur showcase videos including moves and super moves for documentary of dinosaur king
Full Showcase Playlist ( https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLzSUN2_e928Okhjm6IE58QYn_gLUeOBQ1 )

[Dinosaur King - Game by SEGA]
Unoffical gameplay by ShockWave DK
